<br>
mermaid scales - alluring sirens are low teens in level<br>
Griffon Feather - grifawns will drop these they are high teens in level?<br>
Gargoyle eyes - gargoyles are high teens in level<br>
Fire Drake scale - fire drakes are low teens in level<br>
<br>
The broom, torch, shovel, and stein - magicians in the front of nejena are high teens in level<br>
<br>
You can buy the toes from someone camping Gornit or watch <br>
for them at the merchants.<br>
<br>
And then all you have to do is save up for the gems.<br>
<br>
The focus items are well worth it and work on all pets 4-49.  The focus items also give you inteligence and make a decent weapon.  I would suggest doing them as soon as possible.<br>
